    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Two Cheers For Sweatshops</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>In their semi-endorsement of American-run sweatshops overseas, your writers argue that corporate exploitation of labor is a necessary first step in a region's economic growth.</p>
        <p>Although they exhort consumers to make responsible choices to support foreign workers, the authors expect no such responsibility from corporations, in the quest to inflate bloated profit margins with the smallest possible investment in labor.</p>
        <p>Brian Artese  Evanston, Ill.</p>
      </block>
